text: Swedish Grand Prix can refer to: *Swedish Grand Prix, a Formula One motor race *Swedish Summer Grand Prix, an auto race, predecessor of the above Swedish Grand Prix (q.v.) *Swedish Winter Grand Prix, an auto race on the ice of Lake Rämen *Swedish Grand Prix - Class 1, an UIM Class 1 powerboat offshore race *Swedish motorcycle Grand Prix *Speedway Grand Prix of Sweden
title: Swedish Grand Prix (disambiguation)
